---
import CTAButton from './CTAButton.astro';

const problems = [
    {
        icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-8 h-8">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M15 9l-6 6M9 9l6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>`,
        title: 'Lack of Clear Direction',
        subtitle: 'Lost in the Noise',
        desc: `The internet is flooded with tutorials, but piecing them together into a cohesive path feels overwhelming. Without a clear roadmap, you risk wasting years chasing trends instead of building real skills.`,
        impact: '78% of creators quit within 6 months',
        color: 'from-red-500 to-pink-500'
    },
    {
        icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-8 h-8">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M12 12l-3 3M9 12l3 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>`,
        title: 'Struggling to Find Quality Clients',
        subtitle: 'The Client Hunt Nightmare',
        desc: `Finding clients isn't just hard—it's finding the RIGHT ones who value your unique style. Traditional outreach feels like endless grinding, with cold emails ignored and freelancing platforms driving prices to the bottom.`,
        impact: 'Average response rate: 2%',
        color: 'from-orange-500 to-red-500'
    },
    {
        icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-8 h-8">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M21 15l-5-5L5 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M12 8l-2 2M8 12l2-2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>`,
        title: 'Weak Portfolio Recognition',
        subtitle: 'Invisible Among Thousands',
        desc: `Your portfolio doesn't stand out in a sea of similar work. Brands want to see a unique editing style with clear recognition value. They need their products shown in modern, professional visuals that make an impact.`,
        impact: '95% of portfolios look identical',
        color: 'from-yellow-500 to-orange-500'
    },
];
---

<section class='relative w-full py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0a0a0f] via-[#1a1f2e] to-[#0f1419] overflow-hidden'>
    <!-- Background Elements -->
    <div class='absolute inset-0 opacity-20'>
        <div class='absolute top-20 left-20 w-72 h-72 bg-red-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse'></div>
        <div class='absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-64 h-64 bg-orange-500/8 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse delay-1000'></div>
        <div class='absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500/5 to-orange-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl'></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid Pattern -->
    <div class='absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-10'>
        <div class='w-full h-full bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)_0,_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)_1px,_transparent_1px,_transparent_64px),repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)_0,_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)_1px,_transparent_1px,_transparent_64px)]'></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Floating Elements -->
    <div class='absolute top-10 right-10 w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full animate-bounce'></div>
    <div class='absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-1 h-1 bg-orange-400 rounded-full animate-bounce delay-500'></div>

    <div class='container max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10'>
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class='text-center mb-20'>
            <!-- Problem Badge -->
            <div class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500/30 mb-8'>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400">
                    <path d="M12 9v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
                <span class='text-red-400 text-sm font-medium'>The Reality Check</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Main Headline -->
            <h2 class='text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight'>
                Why Most Creators
                <span class='relative'>
                    <span class='bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent'>Struggle</span>
                    <svg class='absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3' viewBox="0 0 200 12" fill="none">
                        <path d="M2 6c50 0 100 0 196 4" stroke="url(#struggle-underline)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="struggle-underline" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                                <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#ef4444"/>
                                <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#f97316"/>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <br />& Never Break Through
            </h2>

            <!-- Problem Description -->
            <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 mb-12'>
                <p class='leading-relaxed'>
                    The creator economy is a <strong class='text-red-400'>thrilling but chaotic</strong> space. Every day, thousands of new voices join the conversation.
                </p>
                <p class='leading-relaxed'>
                    Standing out requires more than talent—it demands <strong class='text-orange-400'>focus, clarity, and a strategy</strong> that sets you apart from the noise.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Shocking Stats -->
            <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16'>
                <div class='p-6 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm'>
                    <div class='text-3xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-2'>89%</div>
                    <div class='text-white/70 text-sm'>of creators earn less than $100/month</div>
                </div>
                <div class='p-6 rounded-xl bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm'>
                    <div class='text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-2'>6 months</div>
                    <div class='text-white/70 text-sm'>average time before giving up</div>
                </div>
                <div class='p-6 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm'>
                    <div class='text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2'>3%</div>
                    <div class='text-white/70 text-sm'>actually build sustainable income</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problems Grid -->
        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16'>
            {problems.map((problem, index) => (
                <div class='group relative'>
                    <!-- Problem Card -->
                    <div class='relative h-full p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/8'>
                        
                        <!-- Content -->
                        <div class='space-y-6'>
                            <!-- Icon -->
                            <div class='w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center'>
                                <div class='text-white/80' set:html={problem.icon} />
                            </div>

                            <!-- Text Content -->
                            <div class='space-y-4'>
                                <div>
                                    <p class='text-white/60 text-sm font-medium mb-2'>{problem.subtitle}</p>
                                    <h3 class='text-xl font-bold text-white leading-tight'>
                                        {problem.title}
                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <p class='text-white/70 leading-relaxed'>
                                    {problem.desc}
                                </p>
                                
                                <!-- Impact Stat -->
                                <div class='pt-4 border-t border-white/10'>
                                    <div class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10'>
                                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-4 h-4 text-white/60">
                                            <path d="M12 9v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                        <span class='text-white/60 text-xs font-medium'>{problem.impact}</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Solution Teaser -->
        <div class='text-center'>
            <div class='inline-block p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-white/5 border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-xl mb-8'>
                <div class='mb-6'>
                    <h3 class='text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4'>
                        But What If There Was a 
                        <span class='bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-yellow-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent'>Better Way?</span>
                    </h3>
                    <p class='text-white/70 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto'>
                        Imagine having a clear roadmap, proven strategies, and a community of creators who've already made it
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class='flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6'>
                    <CTAButton>Discover the Solution</CTAButton>
                    
                    <!-- Trust Indicator -->
                    <div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60'>
                        <div class='flex -space-x-2'>
                            <div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-yellow-400 border-2 border-white/20'></div>
                            <div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-400 border-2 border-white/20'></div>
                            <div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 border-2 border-white/20'></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class='text-sm'>Join 2,500+ successful creators</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
